.SS VERIFY-DISKS
.PP
\f[B]verify-disks\f[]
.PP
The command checks which instances have degraded DRBD disks and
activates the disks of those instances.
.PP
This command is run from the \f[B]ganeti-watcher\f[] tool, which
also has a different, complementary algorithm for doing this check.
Together, these two should ensure that DRBD disks are kept
consistent.
